  "text": "Astro DevRel Newsroom\n\n\nASTRO DEVELOPER UPDATE: JULY 2-5, 2026\n\n20 new releases, including critical fixes, plus shout-outs to 4 first-time contributors, our latest blog post, and a reminder for Astro Launch Week.\n\nHere's a concise overview of recent developments in the Astro ecosystem from July 2-5, 2026.\n\nShipping\n\n\nRELEASE HIGHLIGHTS\n\nWe had 20 releases, including fixes for proxy support in create-astro@5.2.2, a false deprecation warning in astro@7.0.6, 'Go To References' issues in @astrojs/ts-plugin@1.10.10, and Svelte 5 component detection in @astrojs/solid-js@7.0.1.\n\nView release notes https://github.com/withastro/astro/releases/tag/create-astro%405.2.2\n\n• https://github.com/withastro/astro/releases/tag/astro%407.0.6\n\n• https://github.com/withastro/astro/releases/tag/%40astrojs/ts-plugin%401.10.10\n\n• https://github.com/withastro/astro/releases/tag/%40astrojs/solid-js%407.0.1\n\nContributors\n\n\n4 FIRST-TIME CONTRIBUTORS THIS WEEK\n\nShout-outs pulled directly from merged pull requests in the newsletter window.\n\njan-kubica • 2026-06-30\n\nfix: background dev server fails to start in hoisted monorepos https://github.com/withastro/astro/pull/17193\n\ndupontcyborg • 2026-07-01\n\nfix(language-server): bump volar-service-* to 0.0.71 (CVE-2026-33532) https://github.com/withastro/astro/pull/17059\n\nFrancoKaddour • 2026-07-02\n\nfix(@astrojs/solid-js): detect Svelte 5 components using the $$renderer prop https://github.com/withastro/astro/pull/17270\n\nchatman-media • 2026-07-02\n\nFix route generator throwing on a dynamic param value of 0 https://github.com/withastro/astro/pull/17247\n\nCommunity\n\n\nFIRST-TIME CONTRIBUTOR SHOUT-OUTS\n\nA big thank you to our 4 first-time contributors: jan-kubica (dev server fix), dupontcyborg (language-server CVE fix), FrancoKaddour (Solid.js Svelte 5 detection fix), and chatman-media (route generator fix).\n\nOpen contributor PR https://github.com/withastro/astro/pull/17193\n\n• https://github.com/withastro/astro/pull/17059\n\n• https://github.com/withastro/astro/pull/17270\n\n• https://github.com/withastro/astro/pull/17247\n\nEditorial\n\n\nLATEST BLOG POST\n\nJune 2026 - Astro 7, summer swag collection, Astro Germany meetup, and more!\n\nRead the blog post https://astro.build/blog/whats-new-june-2026/\n\nEvents\n\n\nPREVIOUS EVENT THANK YOU\n\nThanks to everyone who joined the Astro Community Call - June 2026 online on 2026-06-24 for community Q&A and project updates.\n\nView event recap https://lu.ma/astro-community-call-june-2026\n\nUpcoming\n\n\nUPCOMING EVENT REMINDER\n\nDon't miss the Astro Launch Week - July 2026 online on 2026-07-08! Join for the kickoff with demos, announcements, and community highlights.\n\nReserve your spot https://lu.ma/astro-launch-week-july-2026\n\nSource metadata\n\nSource project: withastro/astro\n\nWindow: 2026-06-28 to 2026-07-05 (8 days)\n\nRelease count: 20\n\nMerged pull request count: 50\n\nFirst-time contributor count: 4\n\nBlog source: rss\n\nBlog post count: 1\n\nEvent source: local-events-json\n\nMost recent past event: Astro Community Call - June 2026\n\nNext upcoming event: Astro Launch Week - July 2026\n\n----------------------------------------\n\nThat's all for this update! Stay tuned for more.\n\nGenerated 2026-07-06T04:10:21.212Z from withastro/astro. This artifact is Resend-ready but not sent in v1.",
